name: Life Cards!
overview:
Life Cards! designs and prints transparent business cards focused on a clients lifestyle, hobbies, and interests.

Regarded as “more than a business card”, this product is essential for an entrepreneur who wears many hats and prefers not to carry a separate business card for each venture he is involved in. An ideal way to promote your self-brand, this product will separate you from the crowd.

Providing a more in depth view into the personality, Life Cards! emphasizes your passions before your business (unless your business happens to be your passion). These cards a printed on an environmentally friendly transparent PVC, in full color, with endless possibilities.

Visit www.lifecards.biz to learn more.
